@startuml RedirectSequence

'====================================================
' URL System - Redirect Request Sequence
'====================================================

title <size:20><b>URL System - Redirect Request Flow</b></size>\n<size:12>Cache-Aside Pattern with Redis Synchronization</size>

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2E4053
    LifeLineBorderColor #2E4053
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FDFEFE
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E4053
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
    ParticipantFontStyle bold
    ActorBorderColor #1F618D
    ActorBackgroundColor #D6EAF8
    BoxBorderColor #5D6D7E
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8F9F9
}

autonumber "<b>[00]"

actor Client

box "Presentation Layer" #D6EAF8
participant "UrlController" as Controller
end box

box "Business Layer" #D5F5E3
participant "UrlService" as Service
end box

box "Infrastructure Layer" #FCF3CF
database "Redis Cache" as Redis
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
end box

== Incoming Request ==

Client -> Controller : GET /{shortCode}

activate Controller

Controller -> Service : getUrlAndIncrementClicks(shortCode)

activate Service

== Cache Lookup ==

Service -> Redis : Lookup(shortCode)

alt ✅ Cache Hit

    Redis --> Service : Url Object

    note right of Redis
    <b>Cache Hit</b>

    URL retrieved directly
    from Redis.

    ✔ No database read
    ✔ Faster response
    end note

else ❌ Cache Miss

    Redis --> Service : null

    note right of Redis
    <b>Cache Miss</b>

    Requested URL
    not present in cache.
    end note

    Service -> DB : findByShortCode()

    activate DB

    DB --> Service : Url Entity

    deactivate DB

    Service -> Redis : Cache URL\n(TTL = 10 minutes)

end

== Click Analytics ==

note right of Service

<b>Business Logic</b>

• Increment click count

• Keep analytics updated

end note

Service -> Service : clickCount++

== Persist Changes ==

Service -> DB : save(updated Url)

activate DB

DB --> Service : Updated Url

deactivate DB

== Cache Synchronization ==

Service -> Redis : Refresh Cached Object

note right of Redis

<b>Cache Synchronization</b>

Redis now contains
the latest click count.

end note

== Redirect ==

Service --> Controller : Url

deactivate Service

Controller --> Client : HTTP 302 Redirect\nLocation: originalUrl

deactivate Controller

== Request Complete ==

note over Client,DB

<b>Summary</b>

✔ Redis minimizes database reads

✔ PostgreSQL remains the Source of Truth

✔ Click count is persisted

✔ Redis is synchronized after every redirect

end note

@enduml